location.description:
WIEN HADIKGASSE. is a service station with EV charging located in WIEN area.

This service station has a variety of fuel products including Shell V-Power Diesel, Shell Super 95 (E10) and Shell Diesel.

Electric vehicle charging options are also available, including 4 charge points, with CCS with 300.0 kW max power.

This station includes a BILLA Unterwegs and a Toilet.

Food and drinks offerings include Fast Food.
